<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/20419446">行外人对于你的职业都有哪些让你哭笑不得的刻板印象呢？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="348146" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">可以是普遍的刻板印象，也可以是个体的偏见。</div>


